<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śāli 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vāhana śakavarṣaṁbulu 1545 Agu 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nēṭi duṁdhubi saṁvatsara mārggaśira śu 1<unclear>2</unclear> <unclear>bu</unclear> <unclear>śrī</unclear> 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>madrājādhirāja rājaparamēśvara śrī vīra 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>pratāpa śrī vīrarāmadēvarāyalu sāṁbrā 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>jya siṁhyāsanamaṁdu ratna siṁhvāsanārūḍhuḍai <unclear>pṛ</unclear> 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dhivi sāmmrājyaṁbuṁ <supplied reason="omitted">śē</supplied>yucuṁḍaṁgānu peṁmasāni 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tiṁmānāyanigāru <unclear>cevvāku gō</unclear>payaku 
<lb n="9"/>Icina nūtimānyapu śāsanaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> pāpaya pēranu bā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vi nūtanaṁgā toviṁci kaṭṭiṁcē <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> cēnu kha 11 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nīku mānyaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
